"onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,BackRef,WIDTH,175)"
onMouseOut="nd();">3</A>
<SPAN LANG="la" CLASS="Latin">Nuda virtute</SPAN>: <I>cf.</I> <A HREF="
L/Roman/Texts/Grattius/Cynegeticon*.html#153
	"TARGET="Grattius"
onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,1,WIDTH,165)"
onMouseOut="nd();">153
	</A>
<SPAN LANG="la" CLASS="Latin">nudo marte</SPAN> contrasted with <SPAN LANG="la" CLASS="Latin">ex arte</SPAN>.


<P CLASS="ivy">❦</P>


	<P CLASS="justify">
	<A CLASS="note" ID="note4" HREF="
E/Roman/Texts/Grattius/Cynegeticon*.html#ref4
"onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,BackRef,WIDTH,175)"
onMouseOut="nd();">4</A>
<I>i.e.</I> by training they attained to a more convenient and suitable method (<SPAN LANG="la" CLASS="Latin">via</SPAN>) than the old haphazard hunting. For sense of <SPAN LANG="la" CLASS="Latin">propior</SPAN> <I>cf.</I> <A HREF="
http://www.thelatinlibrary.com/cicero/att14.shtml#19
	"TARGET="offsite"
