onMouseOut="nd();">18</A>
Unsatisfying attempts have been made to read <SPAN LANG="la" CLASS="Latin">ire freta</SPAN> and explain it as applicable either to the giants traversing the ocean of the sky in their account on heaven or even to the Argonauts crossing the sea, which is Curcio's strange suggestion.


