	<A HREF="
https://www.hs-augsburg.de/~harsch/Chronologia/Lspost01/Martialis/mar_ep12.html
	"TARGET="offsite"
onMouseOver="return Ebox(EClickHere+'Book 12<BR>of the Epigrams of Martial'+Lat2+LatSearch+'Molossi</SPAN>',WIDTH,195)"
onMouseOut="nd();">
Mart. <SPAN CLASS="small">XII</SPAN>.<SPAN CLASS="smaller">I</SPAN>.1</A>; Claud. <I>Stil.</I> <A HREF="
