<P CLASS="ivy">❦</P>


	<P CLASS="justify">
	<A CLASS="note" ID="note38" HREF="
E/Roman/Texts/Grattius/Cynegeticon*.html#ref38
"onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,BackRef,WIDTH,175)"
onMouseOut="nd();">38</A>
It seems appropriate to take <SPAN LANG="la" CLASS="Latin">his</SPAN> of Molossian dogs rather than of British, as the proper names refer to neighbouring districts of Epirus, Thessaly, Aetolia and Acarnania. Athamania is a district in Epirus near the Pindus range.


<P CLASS="ivy">❦</P>


	<P CLASS="justify">
	<A CLASS="note" ID="note39" HREF="
