onMouseOut="nd();">39</A>
<I>Cf.</I> the qualities suggested in 171‑73, and 156. "Gallic" in 194 may mean "Galatian": see
	<A HREF="
E/Roman/Texts/Grattius/Introduction*.html#note5
"onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,0,WIDTH,175)"
onMouseOut="nd();">
Introduction</A>.


