	<A HREF="
https://archive.org/stream/onomasticon01polluoft#page/n365/mode/2up
	"TARGET="offsite"
onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,2,WIDTH,175)"
onMouseOut="nd();">
Pollux, <SPAN CLASS="small">V</SPAN>.58</A>; Arr. <I>Cyn.</I> 5.9; Colum. <I>R. R.</I> <SPAN CLASS="small">VII</SPAN>.<SPAN CLASS="smaller">XII</SPAN>.4<!--</A>COLUMELLA7-->.


<P CLASS="ivy">❦</P>


	<P CLASS="justify">
