"onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,BackRef,WIDTH,175)"
onMouseOut="nd();">63</A>
C. Atilius Regulus Serranus was consul in 257 and in 250 <SPAN CLASS="small">B.C.</SPAN> He was summoned from farm-work to undertake a military command,
	<A HREF="
L/Roman/Texts/Valerius_Maximus/4*.html#4.5
	"TARGET="Valerius_Maximus"
onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,LatinRef1,WIDTH,155)"
