"onMouseOver="return Ebox(INARRAY,BackRef,WIDTH,175)"
onMouseOut="nd();">64</A>
<SPAN LANG="la" CLASS="Latin">factus</SPAN>, if sound, must have the force of <SPAN LANG="la" CLASS="Latin">instructus</SPAN>.


<P CLASS="ivy">❦</P>


	<P CLASS="justify">
	<A CLASS="note" ID="note65" HREF="
